        </ul>

        <h2 id="leadership-and-operations">Engineering Leadership & Operations</h2>
        <p>
          As a Staff Engineer, my role goes beyond writing code. I guide teams through the entire lifecycle of software systems, ensuring engineering efforts align directly with product outcomes and operational stability:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>System Deconstruction & Monolith-to-Modulith:</strong> Successfully led technical migrations, converting tightly coupled monolithic systems into clean, modular architectures without causing downtime or disrupting product delivery.</li>
          <li><strong>Incident Response & Firefighting:</strong> Guided response teams to resolve critical production outages, building operational observability and automating mitigation tools to ensure outages don't repeat.</li>
          <li><strong>Technical Mentorship:</strong> Championed TDD and domain-driven design practices, leading by example to raise code quality, simplify testing codebases, and increase test coverage to over 95%.</li>
          <li><strong>Product & Stakeholder Collaboration:</strong> Translated complex engineering constraints into clear business trade-offs, enabling product teams to move fast while keeping architectural debt in check.</li>
        </ul>

